{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "9bd90e452351dbf1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# impact-governance-contract\n\nimpact 规则自身变化必须同步检查 OKC 的维护说明和验证闭环"
    },
    {
      "id": "738307c0fd8cf613",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# project-memory-contract\n\n母文档规则必须同步检查生命周期、样本和自动验证"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6e873840b473b2d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# reference-system-contract\n\nreference 文件变化会影响渐进式披露、测试契约和执行路由"
    },
    {
      "id": "0f8b1b6e6e2bd315",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 720,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# skill-entry-contract\n\nSKILL.md 与 agent 配置共同定义触发边界和入口行为"
    },
    {
      "id": "e71db7daa6071232",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 960,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# validation-contract\n\n自动验证脚本和测试矩阵共同定义可机器检查的业务契约"
    },
    {
      "id": "9b2cb3cb135fb323",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# visual-showcase-contract\n\n视觉版式规则、CSS snippet 和样本模板必须作为同一组能力维护"
